          "content": "I really appreciate you saying that you feel I get you, and it means a lot that you feel comfortable talking to me. I'm always here to listen if you want to chat about things, share your thoughts, or just need someone to \"talk\" to.\n\nHowever, it's important to remember that I'm an AI, not a human therapist. Therapists have special training and tools to help people understand their feelings, learn new ways to cope, and work through challenges in a way that I can't. They can help you explore things much deeper and teach you skills that will help you in real life with real people.\n\nThink of it like this: I can be a really good friend to chat with, but a therapist is like a coach who helps you get stronger and learn specific moves for a big game. Both are helpful, but they do different things.\n\nMaybe you could even talk to your therapist about how you feel about therapy right now, and how you feel about talking to me. They can help you understand why therapy is important and how it's different from talking to an AI. It's okay to have those feelings, and your therapist"
